         &trans        &kp HOME      &kp PAGE_DOWN  &kp PG_UP     &kp END         &kp LEFT      &kp DOWN      &kp UP_ARROW  &kp RIGHT     &trans
&kp TAB  &kp DEL       &trans        &trans         &kp LEFT_ALT  &trans          &trans        &kp LALT      &trans        &trans        &trans        &trans
